HEADWORD: Reach
<hw>Reach</hw> <pr>(r⟦emac⟧ch)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To
retch.</def> <rj><au>Cheyne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reach</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
